Use

Give ChatGPT the system spec, key docs, canonical flow JSON, scripts, and parser code in one upload.
Ask ChatGPT for runbooks, troubleshooting, deployment steps, migration reviews, or rollback plans.
Keep the uploaded scope controlled; the manifest shows exactly what was included.
Instructions

Upload the pack zip or the extracted folder.
If the task is migration-related, also upload chatgpt_upload_pack_20260312.md.
In your prompt, state:
your objective
the environment URL
the exact flow/script/file involved
whether you want analysis only or a fix/deploy runbook
Ask for a concrete output, for example:
“Give me a strict runbook”
“Find the likely root cause”
“List rollback steps”
“Review this flow JSON”
Repo rules inside the pack

Sync first: powershell -File scripts/active/bgv_daily_sync.ps1
Verify PAC identity first: pac auth who
Edit only canonical flows in flows/power-automate/unpacked/Workflows/
Do not commit secrets or .env
When flow JSON changes, update linked docs in the same change
Deploy with pac solution pack then pac solution import
